{"tid":1985460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解公務員「政治中立」=「全力支持行政長官」？","createTime":"2020-04-23T07:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:46:22.000Z","uid":195690,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8a2af46df01a87aef53ba66478e04aeb264b168e","tid":1985460,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"呢個咩邏輯嚟？<br />\n<br />\n「根據《公務員守則》，公務員必須保持政治中立，不論本身的政治信念為何，公務員必須對在任的行政長官及政府完全忠誠」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/03/P2019080300763.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F03%2FP2019080300763.htm&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6vTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=d9491182\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/03/P2019080300763.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9VE4di.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9VE4di.png&h=2d4f0d88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d83898e6e08fbac1e1ed4718f36c3011a3c9fc65","tid":1985460,"uid":154054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"因為中立=藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b85706e18df7f1cd87ca5002c5eeec34e93344c","tid":1985460,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:12:46.000Z","msg":"唔熟公務員就可以9up，合符中聯辦既監督原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630844c1b7de3963e3bfc094a933e81da8224096","tid":1985460,"uid":195690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:14:24.000Z","msg":"今日聶德權見記者，係咁講：<br />\n<br />\n「確保公務員政治中立，全力支持特區政府及行政長官」<br />\n<br />\n係有線見到，未有link"},{"pid":"bd137dd317e7503491a569153062fe7afcd418c1","tid":1985460,"uid":195690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚明"},{"pid":"b5bf8ee0b35c9d76ed62e1926e8fb17ce0e585d2","tid":1985460,"uid":233050,"like":0,"dis